Detailed Description

BoxContainer iterator picking items with a specified BlockId.

This iterator runs through all Boxes in a BoxContainer that has the given BlockId. The iterator runs through the Boxes in the order they appear in the BoxContainer, skipping over Boxes that do not have the specified owner rank.
